      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Experience automotive perfection with this absolute gem! This vehicle is in truly mint condition, looking and driving as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine, untouched interior, has been meticulously maintained to the highest standard. If you're looking for a top-tier vehicle that offers a like-new experience, this is the one for you!",
