    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good, dependable condition and has been consistently well-maintained throughout its life. The engine starts reliably every time, and the transmission shifts smoothly, offering a confident driving experience. While the exterior and interior show minor signs of regular use, such as small stone chips and light wear on the driver's seat, the car remains mechanically sound and aesthetically pleasing. It is a solid choice for anyone seeking a reliable daily driver that has been cared for properly.",
