    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by to check out my car! \ud83d\ude97 It has been such a reliable ride and is still in really solid shape, just waiting for its next big adventure. I\u2019ve truly enjoyed driving it and have kept it well-maintained, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road whenever you are. It\u2019s a fantastic deal for anyone who wants a dependable vehicle that still looks and feels great. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I\u2019d love to see this go to a wonderful new home!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 1994 Mazda RX-7 FD features the iconic 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged rotary engine, delivering linear power delivery and high-revving performance. The drivetrain is anchored by a crisp 5-speed manual transmission and a factory Torsen limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution during spirited cornering. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive cooling system overhaul and vacuum line simplification to enhance reliability. The chassis maintains its legendary 50/50 weight distribution and utilizes a sophisticated four-wheel double-wishbone suspension for surgical handling. While the exterior shows minor age-appropriate patina, the internal apex seals show strong compression, and the turbos spool with factory precision.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Clean title. Well-maintained. Reliable performance.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between performance and value. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper reflect its honest road history. Inside, you'll find a smoke-free cabin with premium upholstery that shows only light bolstering wear on the driver\u2019s side. Every button, switch, and digital display functions exactly as intended, including the dual-zone climate control and premium sound system. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly with no leaks or unusual noises; the transmission shifts are crisp and predictable. It has been serviced regularly, with a recent oil change and brake inspection just completed. This car drives straight and true, offering a comfortable yet responsive experience. Sold with a clean title and a full set of service records to provide peace of mind for the next owner.",
      "price": 31500.0,
